message.body: Hey babe, just wondering- did you ever give me back that dress you wore to that dance?
Nope but I shall bring it to you in about an hour
Left the dress and shoes with your mother. THANK YOU SO MUCH THAT GORGEOUS DRESS SAVED ME AND MADE MY DANCE EXPERIENCE SO GOOD I LOVE YOU PLEASE COME BORROW MY CLOTHES SO I FEEL LESS BAD
I have a date thing tuesday with a super cute guy around my age that looks like a total puppy dog and I hate everything I own
I recently invested in a lot of cute dresses. And ooooh what's his name
Uugh perfect His name's Jon, he's a sophomore at drexel and he's a fantastic lindy hopper and he plays soccer and volleyball and draws and is just ADORABLE
Crossing my fingers it goes well
I asked HIM out, which is just crazy
I know! I will totally be coming to raid your closet sometime.
